"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:4.9.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.9.1</span> 标题：乌陵和土明（Urim and Thummim）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<h3 class=\"thlex-subheading\">\n          <strong>乌陵</strong> ：</h3>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אוּרִים</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’urim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:30\">EXO 28:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:8\">LEV 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:21\">NUM 27:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:8\">DEU 33:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:6\">1SA 28:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:63\">EZR 2:63</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:65\">NEH 7:65</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：δῆλος, δήλωσις</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：dēlos, dēlōsis)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir33:3\">SIR 33:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir45:10\">SIR 45:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc2:7\">4MA 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd5:40\">1ES 5:40</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<h3 class=\"thlex-subheading\">\n          <strong>土明</strong> ：</h3>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：תָּמִים</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tamim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:41\">1SA 14:41</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אוּרִים</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tumim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:30\">EXO 28:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:8\">LEV 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:8\">DEU 33:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:63\">EZR 2:63</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:65\">NEH 7:65</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἀλήθεια</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：alētheia)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir45:10\">SIR 45:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd5:40\">1ES 5:40</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>我们不知道乌陵和土明实际上是什么样子。学者有很多提议，包括黑色和白色的小石子，或者某种形式的签。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>大祭司使用这两个物品，按照某种方法来获知上帝的旨意（参<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:21\">NUM 27:21</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:41\">1SA 14:41</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:6\">1SA 28:6</a> 等）。有学者提出，胸袋（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.5.5 胸袋、胸牌 (sacred pocket, breastpiece)&lt;REALIA:4.5.5&gt;</a> ）就像口袋一样盛放着乌陵和土明。祭司向上帝求问是或非时，从袋子里取出的物品就指明了答案。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>古代的译本（如《七十士译本》）倾向于按照字面意思来翻译希伯来文<em>’urim</em> 和<em>tumim</em> ，将其译作“光和完美”，或者抽象地译成“完美的启示”或“完全的光照”。大多数现代译本都对这两个词采取音译，但有些译本（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Moffatt Translation (1926)\">Mft</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> ）将其译作“圣签”，相当充分地传达了这两个词的意思。有些语言可能必须将其译成“上帝的签”。不论采取哪种译法，我们建议附加一个脚注，详细解释这两个词的含义。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:30\">EXO 28:30</a> 添加的脚注如下：“乌陵和土明：祭司用来察验上帝旨意的两个物件；具体使用方法不详。”<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 在这节经文的脚注是：“两个小物件：希伯来文本作‘乌陵和土明’，可能用木头、石头或金属做成，用来按照某种方式获知上帝的回答。”</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:41\">1SA 14:41</a> ，希伯来文本的用词<em>tamim</em> 与<em>tumim</em> 具有相同的辅音，但元音不同。希伯来文本没有<em>’urim</em> 一词。《七十士译本》在这里的文本较长，包含了与<em>’urim</em> 和<em>tumim</em> 对应的词语。关于此处文本问题的讨论和各种译法，参《〈撒母耳记〉手册》（<em>A Handbook on The First and Second Books of Samuel</em> ），第300—301页。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
